data.description:
3br/2.5ba in highly desirable Stoneridge golf community directly across the street from the community park and close proximity to clubhouse and golf amenities!
Master on main level with large closet, large shower, double sink vanity.  
Huge living space with super high ceiling, plenty of light, and stacked-stone gas fireplace.  
Kitchen with breakfast bar, dining room and a great view of park.  SS appliances
Upstairs loft for office or flex space, with 2  additional bedrooms and full guest bath with linen closet.  Great mountain and park views, 
 Covered private patio off the great room is enclosed for pets and has 2 solar tube skylights for added natural light.  Cozy front porch with view and 2 car garage in rear. 
Assumable Mortgage @ 3.75%
